  <br/>


<div class="text text-lg-center">
    <h1 class="display-1 align-content-center" asp-action="Index" style="font-family:serif">InStore</h1>
</div>


<br /><br />
  <section>
      <div class="container">
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
               <center>
                  <h2>Get started with InStore</h2>
               </center>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
               <center>
                  <img width="200px" height="150px" src="https://www.kindpng.com/picc/m/264-2640361_inventory-management-system-png-transparent-png.png"/>
                  <h4>Where we are</h4>
                  <p class="text-justify">We are in more than 25 locations around the world․ We grow thanks to our partners who entrust us with the storage of their products at our various addresses.</p>
                  <a asp-controller="Stores" asp-action="Index">Details</a>
               </center>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
               <center>
                  <img width="200px" height="150px" src="https://www.kindpng.com/picc/m/567-5674919_inventory-management-inventory-management-system-png-transparent-png.png"/>
                  <h4>Become our partner</h4>
                  <p class="text-justify">We cooperate with production companies of different countries, successfully import their products and export to our warehouses. They trust us, what about you.</p>
                  <a href="#partners">Details</a>
               </center>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
               <center>
                  <img width="200px" height="150px" src="https://www.kindpng.com/picc/m/358-3580898_warehouse-clipart-employee-transfer-inventory-clipart-hd-png.png"/>
                  <h4>Our products</h4>
                  <p class="text-justify">Our warehouses store different types of goods, from clothes to food. Depending on the type of product, storage features, they are stored at different addresses.</p>
                  <a asp-controller="Products" asp-action="Index">Details</a>
               </center>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>
